随州市中心医院肿瘤科科长称，“现在肿瘤科的医疗全部都停了，我们科也开始做一线防控，人太少，没办法。
"Now that the oncology department has stopped all medical care, our department has begun to do first-line control, too few people, no way.
”全文1030字，阅读约需2分钟随州癌症患者家属反映，随州及武汉多家医院肿瘤科室因疫情被改造，患者化疗被耽误。
The full text of 1030 words, reading about 2 minutes in Suizhou cancer patients' families, Suizhou and Wuhan hospitals tumor departments have been reformed because of the epidemic situation, patients delayed chemotherapy.
随州市卫健委工作人员称，目前随州市多家医院的肿瘤科室已改成新冠肺炎病区，暂时没有能做化疗的医院，相关情况已向上反映。
At present, the oncology department of many hospitals in Suizhou has been changed to the new crown pneumonia area, and there is no hospital that can do chemotherapy, the relevant situation has been reflected upward.
▲杜女士弟弟的病理报告复印件。
A copy of the pathology report of Ms. Du's brother.
受访者供图━━━━━肿瘤科室改造接收新冠肺炎患者杜女士告诉新京报记者，弟弟今年21岁，是一名在读大学生，今年1月初被查出了恶性肿瘤。
2007-9-25 21: 48 Tumor Unit Reform Reception for New Crown Pneumonia Ms. Du told the Beijing News that her younger brother, a 21-year-old college student, had been diagnosed with a malignant tumor in early January.
1月15日，弟弟在武汉市华中科技大学同济医学院附属同济医院（以下简称武汉同济医院）做了肿瘤切除手术，医生嘱咐三周后回医院做化疗。
On January 15, his younger brother underwent a tumor resection operation at Tongji Hospital, affiliated with Tongji Medical College, Huazhong University of Science and Technology, Wuhan Tongji Hospital.
2月5日，杜女士联系武汉同济医院预约化疗，院方称因疫情，目前已不再接收癌症患者。
On February 5, Ms. Du contacted Wuhan Tongji Hospital to make an appointment for chemotherapy. The hospital said she no longer accepted cancer patients because of the outbreak.
“拖得越久，我们家人心里越忐忑，很担心弟弟因为没办法即时化疗，病情被耽误、进一步恶化。
"The longer we wait, the more scared our family is, worried that the younger brother is unable to chemotherapy, delayed, further deterioration.
” 杜女士说。
"said Mrs. Du.
2月7日，武汉同济医院肿瘤科的一名工作人称，目前医院门诊已关闭，肿瘤科的病房用来接收新冠肺炎病人，该科室部分医生也被调去支援肺炎。
On February 7, a staff member of the oncology department at Wuhan Tongji Hospital said the hospital clinic was closed, the oncology ward was used to receive patients with pneumonia, and some of the department's doctors were called in to help with pneumonia.
“已经差不多两星期没接收癌症患者了。
"I haven't had cancer patients for almost two weeks.
每天有很多癌症患者联系我们，但现在疫情严重，病房不够用。
We have a lot of cancer patients contacting us every day, but we don't have enough wards because of the epidemic.
”上述工作人员称，目前武汉同济医院的主院区作为新冠肺炎的定点医院，两个分院区也开设了发热门诊，“癌症患者本身免疫力就差，新冠肺炎传染性又强，到医院容易交叉感染。
Wuhan Tongji Hospital's main hospital is now the designated hospital for new crown pneumonia, and two sub-hospital districts have set up fever clinics, said the staff. "Cancer patients themselves have poor immunity, new crown pneumonia is infectious and easy to cross-infection.
”━━━━━本地医院接收困难，外地就医路被封无奈，杜女士又联系了随州市唯一的三甲医院——随州市中心医院，该院同样不再接收癌症患者化疗。
-- -- Local hospitals accept the difficulties and the way to medical treatment is blocked, but Ms. Du contacted Suizhou, the only Sanjia hospital in Suizhou, which also no longer receives chemotherapy from cancer patients.
新京报记者从随州市中心医院处得知，肿瘤病区目前已全部改成新冠肺炎专控病区。
Xinjing News reporters from the central hospital in Suizhou City, the oncology area has been converted into the new crown pneumonia control area.
该医院肿瘤科科长称，“现在肿瘤科的医疗全部都停了，我们科也开始做一线防控，人太少，没办法。
"Now that the oncology department has stopped all medical care, our department has also begun to do first-line control, too few people, no way.
”随后，记者咨询了随州市中医医院、曾都医院，均称目前无法接收癌症患者化疗。
"Subsequently, the reporter consulted Suizhou TCM Hospital, Zeng Du Hospital, said that cancer patients are currently unable to receive chemotherapy.
杜女士也曾联系过广州的医院，“但现在路都封了，湖北人去广州那边还要隔离14天，怕耽误化疗。
"But now the road is closed, Hubei people to Guangzhou side of the quarantine for 14 days, afraid of delaying chemotherapy.
”随州市防控指挥部发布的通告显示，城区道路严禁私家车、网约车、出租车上路行驶，对违规出行的，将依据相关法律规定予以顶格处罚。
The notice issued by Suizhou Provincial Command shows that private cars, internet-bound cars and taxis are strictly prohibited from driving on city roads, and those who violate the rules will be punished in accordance with relevant legal provisions.
对于此类癌症患者的化疗困境，湖北省卫健委医政科刘科长表示，随州市医疗资源有限，唯一一家三甲医院也被用来接收新冠肺炎患者，“不是说医院不想接收，是真的没有能力接收，癌症患者的救治、化疗问题也正在向上反映。
The only hospital in Suizhou with limited medical resources is also being used to receive new cases of pneumonia. "Not that hospitals do not want to receive them, they are really unable to accept them, and the treatment and chemotherapy of cancer patients are reflecting upward," said Liu, chief of the medical section of the Hubei Wei Health Commission.
”新京报记者 康佳 实习生 孙朝编辑 康佳 校对 范锦春点击下图进入"全国新型冠状病毒感染肺炎实时地图"值班编辑 吾彦祖 日本载3700人被隔离游轮曝光，船上乘客讲述“海上隔离”关注武汉，也别漏了那些“难上热搜”的城市质疑声中的湖北红会。
2007-9-19 19: 48 China Daily News reporter Kang Jia, editor of the Beijing News, has been checked by Fan Jinchun. At the following table, China's new coronavirus-infected pneumonia has been picked up by Japan's 3,700 people on duty.
